title: nightly-2019-06-10: wf checking is too slow

labels.name: I-compiletime
labels.description: Problems and improvements with respect to compile times.

labels.name: T-compiler
labels.description: Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

body:
STR

1. git clone -b typescript https://github.com/kdy1/swc && (cd swc && git checkout 4d64b3eb5040c5ef9d2d42e93a98e76b9999f24f)

2. Modify swc/.cargo/config to
```toml

[build]
rustflags = [
    "--cfg", "procmacro2_semver_exempt",
    "-Z", "time-passes"
]
 
rustdocflags = [
    "--cfg", "procmacro2_semver_exempt",
]
```

3. cd swc/typescript/checker && cargo check
